des: Daily Health Tips sets you up for success with daily information health and wellness information provide by nutritionists, health care professionals and more. This daily briefing can be short or long, but they are always packed with health and wellness information to help you improve your life. This tool does not provide medical advice, and is for informational and educational purposes only, and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
